            "value": "**Objective:** Act as a Security Analyst conducting vendor security assessment.\n**Context:** Assess security posture for vendor from `${steps.zip_2.id}`.\n**Configurable Input:** Required Certifications: SOC 2 Type II (if handling customer data)\n**Instructions:**\n1. Web search for recent security breaches (past 12 months).\n2. If SOC 2 report found in `${steps.ai_1.response}`, analyze for findings.\n3. List ALL certifications found with dates and expiration status.\n4. Compare found certifications against required list.\n5. Flag missing or expired critical certifications.\n6. Identify any context-based requirements (e.g., healthcare data = HIPAA required).\n**Structured Output Schema:**\n`{ \"recentBreaches\": [{ \"date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", \"description\": \"string\", \"severity\": \"Critical|High|Medium|Low\" }], \"certificationsFound\": [{ \"name\": \"string\", \"date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", \"expirationDate\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", \"status\": \"Valid|Expired|Unknown\" }], \"requiredCertsPresent\": \"boolean\", \"missingCertifications\": [\"array\"], \"expiredCertifications\": [\"array\"], \"soc2Findings\": \"string\", \"securityRiskLevel\": \"High|Medium|Low\", \"securityTeamFlag\": \"boolean\", \"flagReason\": \"string\" }`"
